title: Ep - 5 - Mark Long from Road Rules Season 1
description:
Kate interviews Mark Long from the first season of Road Rules about how he was cast for the show and what it is like looking back on his MTV experience 20 years later, West Coast Bravo.com reporter Paul Zahn directs Toddlers and Tiaras, and Kate and her friend Scott discuss the premier episode of Chasing Kelce.
